Agenda:

6:00 - 7:00 phone bank or campaign work in the office
7:00 - 7:15 events, review of recent events (what to change)
7:15 - 7:30 upcoming events and activities.
7:30 open discussion

*any items that should be on the agenda can be added - contact me by email *

The meeting will be held at campaign headquarters. We will meet in Nashua for car pooling at 5:15 (at Border's Books).

The name for the group's YouTube account will be decided and a Ron Paul book will be awarded.

This will be an opportunity to help the campaign in several ways in one meeting.

The donations will be applied to an order of Ron Paul 2008 DVDs or constitutions.
